      <link href="/2024/09/28/Hexo%E4%BC%98%E9%9B%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9/"/>
      <url>/2024/09/28/Hexo%E4%BC%98%E9%9B%85%E7%9A%84%E4%B9%A6%E5%86%99%E6%96%87%E7%AB%A0-%E6%A8%A1%E6%9D%BF%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<style>r { color: Red }o { color: Orange }gn { color: Green }y { color: yellow }b { color: blue }gy { color: gray }</style><h1 id="引言"><a href="#引言" class="headerlink" title="引言"></a>引言</h1><p><strong>发现一个问题，每次<mark class="hl-label blue">hexo</mark> <mark class="hl-label blue">new</mark> 的时候<mark class="hl-label blue">Front-matter</mark> 中内容少的可怜，那怎么修改默认的格式呢？</strong></p><h1 id="实现"><a href="#实现" class="headerlink" title="实现"></a>实现</h1><p><strong>只要去主目录下找到<mark class="hl-label blue">scaffolds</mark> 文件夹下找到一个<mark class="hl-label blue">post.md</mark> 文件修改即可</strong></p><h1 id="范例"><a href="#范例" class="headerlink" title="范例"></a>范例</h1><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">标题</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title</span>: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">date</span>: &#123;&#123; date &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author</span>: </span><br><span class="line">简述</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">summary</span>:</span><br><span class="line">使用自定义封面 </span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">img</span>: </span><br><span class="line">是否置顶<span class="literal">true</span>，或者去掉</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">top</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">轮播</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">cover</span>:</span><br><span class="line">轮播图</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">coverImg</span>: </span><br><span class="line">标签</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">tags</span>: </span><br><span class="line">分类</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">categories</span>: </span><br><span class="line">是否加密文章，<span class="title class_">SHA256</span>加密</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">password</span>: </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
      
